---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import homeArt from '../assets/home-deterministic-random-walk-art.png';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="home">
			<h1 class="sr-only">Deterministic Random Walk</h1>
			<section class="intro" aria-label="Site introduction">
				<div class="intro-copy">
					<p class="kicker">Deterministic Random Walk</p>
					<p class="lead">
						Life, markets, and human systems move through noise. The work is not to pretend
						the randomness disappears, but to discover the few rules, values, and processes
						that keep holding while everything else shifts.
					</p>
					<p>
						That is also how I think about AI for investment work. Probabilistic models are
						powerful because they can judge meaning in ambiguous places. Deterministic
						engineering is what makes those judgments repeatable, auditable, and useful in
						production.
					</p>
					<p>
						This site is a small notebook on modernizing investment processes with
						production-grade AI: art where uncertainty is real, science where reliability is
						non-negotiable, and the discipline of combining both.
					</p>
					<nav class="home-links" aria-label="Primary pages">
						<a href="/blog">Read the blog</a>
						<a href="/about">About me</a>
					</nav>
				</div>
				<figure class="intro-art">
					<Image
						src={homeArt}
						width={420}
						alt="A fixed rabbit template surrounded by energetic hand-drawn circles."
					/>
					<figcaption>
						A fixed template inside wild circles: one small picture of the whole idea.
					</figcaption>
				</figure>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.home {
		width: min(1040px, calc(100% - 2em));
		padding: 3.5em 1em 4em;
	}
	.intro {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(280px, 0.8fr);
		gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		align-items: center;
	}
	.intro-copy {
		max-width: 680px;
	}
	.kicker {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.85em;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	.lead {
		margin: 0 0 1.1em;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
		font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 4vw, 2.35rem);
		line-height: 1.16;
	}
	.intro-copy p:not(.kicker):not(.lead) {
		max-width: 620px;
		margin: 0 0 1.05em;
		font-size: 1.02em;
		line-height: 1.68;
	}
	.home-links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1.4em;
	}
	.home-links a {
		text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
		font-weight: 700;
	}
	.intro-art {
		margin: 0;
	}
	.intro-art img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 420px;
		margin-left: auto;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}
	.intro-art figcaption {
		max-width: 420px;
		margin: 0.75em 0 0 auto;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.82em;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}
	@media (max-width: 820px) {
		.home {
			padding-top: 2em;
		}
		.intro {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.intro-art img,
		.intro-art figcaption {
			margin-left: 0;
		}
	}
</style>
